//Pseudocode for making coffee
//Make sure both the coffee grinder and the coffeemaker are plugged in
//Using the coffee scoop already with the coffee beans, put 6 scoops of beans into the grinder
//replace top of grinder and press down the grind button until the beans are well ground
//place coffee filter into basket at top of coffeemaker
//dump coffee grounds into filter
//fill coffee carafe with water from the sink up to the 10 cup mark
//pour water into coffeemaker water reservoir
//replace carafe in its spot
//on the coffeemaker, press "Brew"
//when the coffeemaker beeps, pour coffee into coffee mug
//replace carafe in its spot
//wait until coffee is cool enough to drink
//enjoy drinking fresh coffee from your mug!
